cellularAutomata.cellState.model
Class NCellState

java.lang.Object
  cellularAutomata.cellState.model.CellState
      cellularAutomata.cellState.model.NCellState

public class NCellState
extends CellState

A cell state for a cellular automaton with values 0 through N-1. The maximum possible number of states is limited only by the system's maximum integer value, but more than 256 states cannot be displayed because the colors will overlap.

Author:
David Bahr
